{"tid":34283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾車咁都贏到西布朗我比狗屌屎眼","createTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:29:15.000Z","uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1642022030609b4722eb8ded96fc9e3675c0010","tid":34283,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"今場真心垃圾車真係無乜可能贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先西布朗近4場真係fit到爆 3勝1和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話就係話垃圾車主場 但有睇上場對鏝都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雷斯比阿古獸收山腳 邊有咁快恢復到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且哥斯達 柏度上場好似都傷傷地 真係會失哂態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都仲未講馬迪岩岩出番 邊到keep得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以垃圾車今晚一定比西布朗炒456<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f1d1b7bc12a5a8041a6ade7801b2f00d6a9f7c","tid":34283,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"手足想發達可以allin西布朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c8de48138494194cd8922b064763f9381d7a15","tid":34283,"uid":26467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"比啲咁既對手西布朗... is 侮辱"},{"pid":"b8c62a510df160071ab080a28ddeb36ee4bfa7e2","tid":34283,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比啲咁既對手西布朗... is 侮辱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真"},{"pid":"00b41db9e2935e5fe5969222c46f4a1ed867028f","tid":34283,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3c906cd4eb1baa561fbdc94014ccfaa64af7d9","tid":34283,"uid":1514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201